        {
          "type": "final",
          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "The Phase 3 plan is directly citing ADR decisions from task descriptions (`ADR D1 / D1.1`, and similarly in every task). `knowledge/conventions/pre-track-adr-authoring.md` says impl-plan artifacts must reference spec/type catalogues rather than ADRs directly, because direct `impl-plan -> ADR` citation skips the SoT chain. This leaves the plan artifact with the wrong layer placement; remove the ADR citations from task descriptions and rely on the IN/CN/AC spec refs instead.",
